get current site "MAY 2013" WordPress Codex "Function Reference"
================================================================

NAME
----

get current site - Gets the current site based on the value of the \$current\_site global

SYNOPSIS
--------

Gets the current site based on the value of the \$current\_site global
variable.

USAGE
-----

` <?php get_current_site(); ?> `

PARAMETERS
----------

None

RETURN VALUES
-------------

 (Object) 
:   Returns current site object.

SOURCE FILE
-----------

`get_current_site()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-functions.php`.

SEE ALSO
--------

See also index of [Function
Reference](/Function_Reference "Function Reference") and index of
[Template Tags](/Template_Tags "Template Tags").

